  "title": "Clinic Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Support daily clinic operations by handling administrative tasks, assisting in basic clinical duties, and ensuring a smooth patient experience. The role requires good organizational skills, attention to detail, and strong communication abilities to interact well with both patients and medical staff.</p><p></p><p><strong>Clinic Operating Hours:</strong></p><p>Monday-Friday 8.30am-5.30pm</p><p>Saturday 8.30am-12.30pm</p><p></p><p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>1. Administrative Duties</p><p>2. Patient Care and Support</p><p>3. Customer Service & Communication</p><p>4. Clinical Assistance</p><p>5. Cleanliness & Safety Compliance</p><p></p><p><strong>Eligibility:</strong> minimum 1 year experience in a private specialist clinic required.</p>",
